item.title: The Power of Good Design and the Adventure Continues: Legends of the Yucatán Part 5 | Episode 91
item.description: In this episode, we dive into the power of good design with special guest Mr. Tim Mills, a local artist and designer. Join host Mr. Jason and co-hosts Miya and Frank as we explore how design shapes the way we interact with products, brands, and the world around us. From brilliant everyday designs to products that could use a serious upgrade, we’ll discuss what makes good design truly impactful and why it matters more than ever...
